Core Capabilities
- Supports custom multiplayer servers for Grand Theft Auto V with extensive modding capabilities.
- Offers a robust scripting engine with support for Lua and C# for custom game logic.
- Enables seamless integration of custom assets, including vehicles, maps, and scripts.
- Features advanced server management tools with real-time performance monitoring capabilities.
- Enables cross-platform play, supporting both Windows and Linux server environments.

